        "timestamp": "2020-02-19 14:19:13.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis patch is used to update the out-of-date certifcate of cds ui. Now the certifcate has changed to pkcs12 and passphrase instead of the key certifcate in previous versions. The reason is AAF init container auto-generated key file has permission 0400 for root user and cds-ui won't be able to read the key file with node user. \n\nAnother change is to use the envrionment variables for the keyfile and passphrase file, it would be eaiser to set the variables to point to auto-generated AAF files or use the secret configmap.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
